WEBVTT

00:07.081 --> 00:08.349
<i>Previously on The Affair...</i>

00:08.350 --> 00:09.919
Mom, this is Furkat.

00:09.920 --> 00:11.121
<i>Are you two working together?</i>

00:11.122 --> 00:12.758
I'm his assistant.

00:12.759 --> 00:14.662
<i>You can tell me how
what you're doing</i>

00:14.663 --> 00:16.265
<i>is any different... you know,
Vik living in your basement,</i>

00:16.265 --> 00:18.135
<i>paying you rent, while
also fucking you.</i>

00:18.136 --> 00:20.139
<i>I don't mention one lunch
and that's a problem?</i>

00:20.140 --> 00:21.441
What about you driving two hours

00:21.442 --> 00:22.978
to see your ex without telling me?

00:22.979 --> 00:24.314
Yeah, I never should've told you!

00:24.315 --> 00:25.517
You live in the fucking basement,

00:25.518 --> 00:26.686
and you come up when you feel like it;

00:26.687 --> 00:28.155
You stay down when you feel like it.

00:28.156 --> 00:30.026
<i>It's what you said you wanted.</i>

00:30.027 --> 00:31.796
<i>Because I thought
that's what you wanted.</i>

00:31.797 --> 00:33.633
<i>Home, sweet home. I
do have one request.</i>

00:33.634 --> 00:35.069
I know. You don't have to say it.

00:35.070 --> 00:36.639
I'm done with him, really.

00:36.640 --> 00:37.708
Okay.

00:37.709 --> 00:39.177
<i>Is Noah here?</i>

00:39.178 --> 00:40.981
I'm concerned about him
because he was stabbed

00:40.982 --> 00:42.317
and now he's MIA.

00:42.318 --> 00:44.054
Why does he still matter so much to you?

00:44.055 --> 00:45.724
What?

00:45.725 --> 00:47.761
I could never figure out if
you're just so narcissistic

00:47.762 --> 00:49.230
that you weren't paying attention.

00:49.231 --> 00:51.401
- Excuse me?
- Our mother had just died.

00:51.402 --> 00:55.076
Noah was using you to
get the fuck away from us.

00:55.077 --> 00:56.913
<i>- My dad died.
- Did your dad</i>

00:56.914 --> 00:58.717
<i>- leave you anything?
- His house.</i>

00:58.718 --> 01:00.453
<i>When was the last
time you were there?</i>

01:00.454 --> 01:01.623
<i>Twenty years ago.</i>

01:01.624 --> 01:03.960
<i>My mother died there.</i>

01:03.961 --> 01:05.831
<i>I think I know who attacked me.</i>

01:05.832 --> 01:08.402
<i>He's a guard at Fishkill
named John Gunther.</i>

01:08.403 --> 01:10.039
<i>He's been following
me since I got out.</i>

01:10.040 --> 01:11.174
- Fuck you!
- Dad?

01:11.175 --> 01:12.410
Martin, what...

01:12.411 --> 01:13.880
<i>Solloway?</i>

01:13.881 --> 01:15.149
I'm gonna hang on to this for safety.

01:15.150 --> 01:16.485
- Come on, don't...
- Hey!

01:20.394 --> 01:21.729
<i>Dad, are you okay?</i>

01:21.730 --> 01:23.232
<i>Yeah, I'm fine.</i>

01:23.233 --> 01:25.771
Either of you remember
a-a guy named Gunther?

01:25.772 --> 01:28.943
<i>Yeah, his folks own that
hunting store off 76.</i>

01:28.944 --> 01:31.014
Noah, you don't look so good.

01:33.888 --> 01:35.691
Fuck!

01:35.692 --> 01:37.093
What the fuck is wrong with you?

01:37.094 --> 01:38.596
You're such a fucking mess.

01:38.597 --> 01:40.300
Martin, get up.

01:41.469 --> 01:42.871
Martin?

01:42.872 --> 01:44.909
Martin! Stop!

01:44.910 --> 01:46.211
Martin!

